After completing this course you will be able to :

Explore essential libraries for deep learning, such as NumPy, Matplotlib, and SciPy.

Build, train and deploy your first neural network with Tensorflow that can correctly classify fashion images.

Create more powerful and complex models for better accuracy.

Analyze and improve the performance of the training model using hyperparameter tuning and optimization.

Compare between different architectures of a convolutional neural network that can solve complex image classification tasks.

Build and train Recurrent Neural Networks (RNNs).

Compare between RNN variants such as GRUs and LSTMs.

Utilize word embedding algorithms to generate numeric representations of text.

Implement recurrent neural networks (RNNs) to classify movie reviews based on sentiment.
